Code preview of the table BC_展位子品牌系列变更表

alter table "BC_BrandSeriesChange"
drop constraint FK_BC_BRAND_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH;

drop table "BC_BrandSeriesChange" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_BrandSeriesChange" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_BrandSeriesChange"
(
"BrandSeriesChangeID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"StoreyID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"ContractCode" VARCHAR(20),
"IsCreateContract" INTEGER,
"NewContractPrice" DECIMAL(20, 2),
"NewContractStartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"NewContractEndTIme" TIMESTAMP,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Status" INTEGER,
"UpdatetTime" TIMESTAMP,
"IsAbolish" INTEGER,
constraint PK_BC_BRANDSERIESCHANGE primary key ("BrandSeriesChangeID")
);

comment on column "BC_BrandSeriesChange"."Status" is
'拟子品牌系列变更
合同创建
已取消（合同取消）
已有效（合同生效）
已完成（不创建合同并更新至经营图）
已废除（方案废除）
注：多个状态流程（签合同、不签合同）';

alter table "BC_BrandSeriesChange"
add constraint FK_BC_BRAND_REFERENCE_BC_BOOTH foreign key (BCID)
references "BC_BoothChange" (BCID);
